'''埃涅迪·伊尔迪科'''（{{lang-hu|'''Enyedi Ildikó'''}}，{{bd|1955年|11月15日}}），[[匈牙利|匈牙利]]女导演和编剧，至今执导了九部影片。

==事业==
1989年作品 ''[[My_20th_Century|Az én XX. századom]]'' 获得[[戛纳影展|戛纳影展]][[金摄影机奖|金摄影机奖]]。<ref name="festival-cannes.com">{{cite web |url=http://www.festival-cannes.com/en/archives/ficheFilm/id/150/year/1989.html |title=Festival de Cannes: My 20th Century |accessdate=2009-08-02 |work=festival-cannes.com |archive-date=2012-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121003194014/http://www.festival-cannes.com/en/archives/ficheFilm/id/150/year/1989.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>1992年她担任[[第42届柏林影展|第42届柏林影展]]评审<ref name="Berlinale">{{cite web |url=http://www.berlinale.de/en/archiv/jahresarchive/1992/04_jury_1992/04_Jury_1992.html |title=Berlinale: 1992 Juries |accessdate=2011-03-27 |work=berlinale.de |archive-date=2019-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190418173956/https://www.berlinale.de/en/archiv/jahresarchive/1992/04_jury_1992/04_Jury_1992.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1994年作品《{{link-en|魔幻獵人|Magic Hunter}}》入选[[第51届威尼斯影展|第51届威尼斯影展]]主竞赛片<ref>{{cite news|last1=Giovanna Grassi, Tullio Kezich|title=Venezia, Stone in gara fra tanti " deb "|url=http://archiviostorico.corriere.it/1994/luglio/29/Venezia_Stone_gara_fra_tanti_co_0_9407296797.shtml|accessdate=2015-10-21|work=[[晚邮报|Corriere della Sera]]|date=1994-07-29|archive-date=2015-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151106232202/http://archiviostorico.corriere.it/1994/luglio/29/Venezia_Stone_gara_fra_tanti_co_0_9407296797.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2007年担任第29届[[莫斯科影展|莫斯科影展]]评审<ref name="Moscow2007">{{cite web |url=http://www.moscowfilmfestival.ru/miff34/eng/archives/?year=2007 |title=29th Moscow International Film Festival (2007) |accessdate=2013-04-22 |work=MIFF |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130421051129/http://www.moscowfilmfestival.ru/miff34/eng/archives/?year=2007 |archivedate=2013-04-21 }}</ref>。

2017年电影《[[肉與靈|-{zh-cn:肉与灵;zh-hk:夢鹿情緣;zh-tw:夢鹿情謎}-]]》获得[[第67届柏林影展|第67届柏林影展]][[金熊奖|金熊奖]]<ref name="Golden">{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2017/film/news/berlinale-berlin-film-festival-2017-winners-full-list-1201992021/|title=Berlin Film Festival: ‘On Body and Soul’ Wins Golden Bear for Best Film|accessdate=2017-02-18|work=Variety|archive-date=2020-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201018070426/https://variety.com/2017/film/news/berlinale-berlin-film-festival-2017-winners-full-list-1201992021/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

